Enum SqlStatement.Type

    SqlStatement

    public static enum SqlStatement.Type
extends Enum<SqlStatement.Type>
    The approximate JDBC type of a column.

    This type affects which ResultSet method we use to get values of this column: the default is ResultSet.getObject(int), but we'd prefer to use native values getInt and getDouble if possible.
